description: Curbside PHO is serving up some of the most delicious and authentic Vietnamese cuisine you can find on the roads of SoCal. The curbside chefs simply simmer up a savory beefy broth that’s flavored to perfection. From there, you’re able to build your own tasty Pho creation. You can choose either egg or rice noodles, then choose the perfect premium meat; pork, chicken, meatballs, or beef, and then make your succulent soup complete with a few of these veggies; green & white onions, peppers, or bean sprouts. Now you undoubtedly have a most phenomenal pho. So for your next meal, Curbside PHO is the most flavorful way to go, fo sho.
name: Curbside PHO
